Package: catnip
Version: 3.3.2.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Electronic Cats <support@electroniccats.com>
Depends: python3, libusb-1.0-0, openocd
Homepage: https://github.com/ElectronicCats/CatSniffer-Tools/
Description: All in one CatSniffer tools — multi-protocol RF sniffer CLI
 CatSniffer is a multi-protocol RF sniffer for 2.4GHz and sub-GHz frequencies.
 This tool allows you to sniff BLE, Zigbee, Thread, LoRa and more using the
 CatSniffer hardware. It also provides a VHCI bridge to expose the device
 as a standard Linux HCI controller.
